high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife with yellow handle.
Turn around and move across the room to the microwave.
Open the microwave then slice the apple beside the egg in 3 pieces and remove one of the slices, then close the microwave.
Put the apple slice in the sink below the microwave.
Put the knife with yellow handle down
Open the microwave above the sink.
Get a second slice of the apple, close the microwave.
Turn around then move across the room to the fridge.
Open fridge, place apple beside the potato on the shelf, close the fridge and open it again then pick up the apple slice. Close the fridge
Turn to the right and go to counter left of the stove.
Place the apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Get a  apple from the microwave, slice it then put on counter.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Take the knife with the yellow handle from the counter.
Turn around, go to the sink.
Cut the apple in the microwave above the sink.
Stay in front of the sink.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Stay in front of the sink.
Take a piece of apple from the microwave.
Turn around, go to the refrigerator.
Put the apple on the shelf next to the potato in the fridge. Close and open the fridge door. Take the apple piece from the fridge.
Go to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Put the piece of apple on the counter in between the two forks and close to the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold piece of apple on a counter.

high_descs: Step backward and turn left, then turn right to face the white counter next to the stove.
Take the long knife with a yellow handle from the white counter.
Turn around and walk across to the sink. Hold up the knife.
Open the microwave above the sink. Cut the apple inside the microwave into half. Put half the apple into the sink. Then cut the apple inside the microwave into half and close the microwave door.
Place the knife onto the counter next to the sink. Then take it back up.
Open the microwave door and break open the potato inside the microwave with the knife staying inside the potato. Close the microwave door.
Turn to the apple in the sink.
Open the microwave door and take a quarter of the apple out. Close the microwave door.
Hold the apple piece and turn right, then left and walk across to the fridge. Open the fridge door.
Open the fridge door and put the apple piece into the fridge. Close the fridge door. After 5 minutes, open the fridge and take out the apple piece and close the fridge door.
Turn right to the white counter next to the fridge.
Place the apple piece on the white counter.
anns.task_desc: Place an apple piece on the white counter next to the fridge.
